// auth_dialog.npk — SSH auth dialog driver (v0.8.2)
//
// Runs the auth loop for a single pane, popping GTK dialogs as needed.
// Called from terminal_widget.npk on_draw when an SSH session is awaiting auth.
//
// Designed as a cooperative state machine: call auth_dialog_tick(pane_id)
// each frame. Returns AUTH_DIALOG_DONE when done (success or failure).

